Frequently Asked Questions

Why is knowing my genetic profile necessary?

Genetic sequencing will allow us to design a program for YOU. Every single human has a different genetic sequence and predisposition for disease. By knowing this, we will be able to prevent many diseases from developing. Genetic analysis will allow us to know both your genetic advantages and disadvantages. We will know what you are likely to develop and will be able to intervene before the disease develops.
